# Analytical Cashbook

This will show your how to create cashbook in Microsoft excel.

1. Create 3 sheets in excel namely 
   *  FILE, 
   *  ANALYTICAL, 
   *  RECEIPT AND PAYMENT,
   
2. In the FILE sheet is where we setup the accounts.
